Right.

1315
01:10:30.935 --> 01:10:33.473
(Mike) 'Hey. there's three ways in here.
there's three of us.'

1316
01:10:33.688 --> 01:10:35.805
'We watch each other's
backs. huh?'

1317
01:10:36.190 --> 01:10:37.190
