Maybe there's another way in.

1465
01:22:50.466 --> 01:22:54.585
It's kinda dark.
I don't see anything.

1466
01:22:55.262 --> 01:22:57.379
There's gotta be
a security guard on duty.

1467
01:22:58.223 --> 01:23:00.966
Well. let's try and.
uh. wake him up!

1468
01:23:01.310 --> 01:23:03.267
[siren blaring]

1469
